description:
Well this is a first for me. I've had worlds get messed up from patches or get chunk errors... but never completely fail before. I'm guessing something got stuck in an infinite loop, causing the the frame rate to drop to like 1 frame every 5 to 10 seconds.

So basically I have reverted back to where we were at Episode #109. Not to worry though, I am quickly recovering from the loss.
